if statements => conditional statements

 - control flow: execute logic based on the condition met 
 
 - if/else statements 
 
 - if (condition) 
    logic to be executed 
   elsif (second condition)
    logic to be executed 
   elsif (second condition)
    logic to be executed 
   else 
    logic to be execute 
   end 
   
   
